Have you updated your trackers? 'Cause this one says just 
"http://eztv.tracker.thepiratebay.org/announce

udp://eztv.tracker.thepiratebay.org:80/announce"

So try adding:

http://tracker.thepiratebay.org/announce

udp://tracker.thepiratebay.org:80/announce

http://tracker.openbittorrent.com/announce

udp://tracker.openbittorrent.com:80/announce

(right click and press Properties and paste these)

I don't really understand how those things work, but I'm assuming that the trackers for The Pirate Bay & BitTorrent contribute in some way so maybe they'll help. :)
